16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．掌握霍曼转移轨道的设计方法，以及轨道摄动和轨道保持与控制的概念。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．了解火箭发动机的工作原理，掌握齐奥尔科夫斯基公式的理论推导。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．了解航天器姿态控制中各类敏感器与姿态执行机构的工作原理，掌握航天器姿态的确定与控制方法。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．掌握<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">航天器有效载荷的定义<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，以及航天任务与轨道选择的关系。了解航天器再入返回的方式及其特点。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《航天技术基础》第二部分<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《工程热力学》<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分）<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基本概念 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热力系、界面与外界、平衡状态、状态参数、过程量、热量与功、状态方程、表压与真空度、分压力、可逆过程与不可逆过程、理想气体与实际气体、熵变、熵流、熵产、音速、马赫数、滞止参数、节流及焦耳<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">-<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">汤姆逊效应、余隙容积、压缩因子、饱和状态、未饱和水与过热蒸汽、湿蒸汽、流体的临界状态与流动的临界状态、循环净功与循环净热量、循环热效率、制冷系数与制热系数等。 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基本定律 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热力学第一定律； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热力学第二定律；<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）熵方程； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">卡诺定律、卡诺循环和克劳修斯积分式内容及应用； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热能中的可用能及其不可逆损失分析。 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">常用工质热力性质 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理想气体性质及其计算； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理想混合气体性质及其计算； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">水蒸气热力性质的图表计算法； <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热力过程、热力循环以及气体流动 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">热力过程的状态参数、热量与功的计算及其图示。 &nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">充放气过程分析； &nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">气体流动过程的分析；<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基本蒸汽动力循环分析计算及其提高热效率的主要措施； <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5) <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基本气体动力循环的分析计算及其提高热效率的主要措施。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《航天技术基础》第三部分<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《机械原理》<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分）<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">机械原理研究的对象和内容。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平面机构的组成和运动简图的绘制；平面机构自由度；平面机构的组成原理及结构分析。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用速度瞬心法进行机构的速度分析；用相对运动图解法进行机构的运动分析；用解析法进行机构的运动分析。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">移动副、螺旋副、转动副中的摩擦和自锁；机械的效率与自锁的关系。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平面四杆机构的基本类型及其演化；平面连杆机构的工作特性；平面连杆机构的设计。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6.<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">凸轮机构的应用与分类；从动件的运动规律及绘制；用图解法设计凸轮的轮廓曲线；用解析法设计凸轮的轮廓曲线及刀具加工的轨迹；凸轮机构基本尺寸的确定（基圆半径与压力角的关系、滚子半径与凸轮的关系、平底从动件的平底长度的确定）。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．齿轮机构的优缺点；齿廓啮合基本定律及共轭齿廓；渐开线的形成、特性及渐开线齿廓的啮合；渐开线标准直齿圆柱齿轮的参数和尺寸计算；渐开线直齿圆柱齿轮的啮合过程、正确啮合条件、中心距、连续传动的条件；渐开线齿廓的切齿方法和原理；渐开线齿廓发生根切的原由及不发生根切的方法；变位齿轮的加工原理、尺寸参数；变位齿轮传动的类型；平行轴斜齿圆柱齿轮机构和圆锥齿轮机构齿廓的形成、参数和尺寸计算、当量齿轮；蜗杆机构齿廓的形成、参数和尺寸计算。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．轮系的分类和应用；定轴轮系、周转轮系和混合轮系的传动比计算；行星轮系各轮齿数的选配条件。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">9<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．棘轮机构、槽轮机构、不完全齿轮机构、凸轮间歇运动机构、万向节连轴节机构、螺旋机构的组成和工作原理。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">10<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．周期性速度波动调节中飞轮的设计原理。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">11<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．机械平衡的目的及类型；刚性转子的平衡原理、不平衡量的测定及平衡精度；简单介绍刚性转子的平衡实验；平面机构的静平衡。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">12. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">机器的机械效率和自锁。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">13. <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">机器的等效动力学模型；运动学方程建模；飞轮设计。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">参考书目录：<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%;\"><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">[1] <\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">褚桂柏，《航天技术概论》，中国宇航出版社，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2002<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">.<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">[<\/span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">]<\/span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">沈维道，《工程热力学》，高等教育出版社，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2007<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">;<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Ro