font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">考试大纲<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">本考试涵盖“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">航天航天概论<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">”、“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">空气动力学<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">”和“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">飞行器环境控制<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">”三门课程，考生选择其中两门进行考试。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">报考“飞行器设计”、“直升机工程”方向的考生建议选择“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">航天航天概论<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">”和“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">空气动力学<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">”；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:38px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">报考“人机与环境工程”方向的考生建议选择“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">航天航天概论<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">”和“<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">飞行器环境控制<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family: 宋体\">”。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">一、《航空航天概论》部分<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">1.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">飞行器（包含航空器和航天器）的发展史和分类；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">2.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">典型航空器和航天器的主要组成部分；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">3.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">机翼产生升力的原理、升力公式、增升装置类别及原理、飞行阻力类别和减阻措施；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">4.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">风洞类别、风洞试验相似性要求；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">5.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">飞机的飞行性能指标、操作性与稳定性的实现；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">6.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">航空发动机工作原理和典型结构；<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\"> <\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">7.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">常用航空仪表和导航设备工作原理。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 150%;font-family:宋体\">二、《空气动力学》部分<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">1.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">流体介质、气动力和力矩、控制体与流体微团等概念；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">2.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">流体运动基本方程的建立；迹线、流线、流函数、速度位、旋涡运动概念；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">3.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">伯努利方程及应用；点源、偶极子、点涡等基本解叠加、库塔<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">-<\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">儒可夫斯基升力定理；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">4.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">一维等熵绝热流；马赫波与膨胀波、正激波、斜激波基本概念、喷管流动；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">5.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">层流与湍流等粘流特性与基本概念；<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">6.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">计算流体力学和实验空气动力学基本概念。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">三、《飞行器环境控制》部分<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">1.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">航空生理学<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">2.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">座舱环境设计标准<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">3.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">飞行器环境控制系统<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">4.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">加温与制冷系统、制冷附件<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">5.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">气流组织分配<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">6.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">电子设备冷却<\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%\">7.<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">环控系统设计与应用实例<\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height:150%;color:red\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\"><br/><\/span><br/><\/p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\"><br/><\/span><\/strong><br/><\/p>","2F6DD47251D72649E0632D1E000A854B":"<p><strong><span style=\";font-family:Arial;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">参考书目<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">袁春风《计算机组成与系统结构（第<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">版）》，清华大学出版社，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">20<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">22<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">年<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">月<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">谭志虎<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">《<\/span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计算机组成原理（微课版）<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">》，<\/span><a href=\"https://book.douban.com/press/2609\"><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人民邮电出版社<\/span><\/span><\/a><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">，<\/span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\">2021<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">年<\/span><span style=\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\">3<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">月<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">王党辉，康继昌，安建峰译《计算机组成与设计<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">硬件<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">/<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">软件接口<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">(<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">版<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">)<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">》，机械工业出版社，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2015<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><strong><span style=\";font-family:Arial;font-size:12px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><\/p><p><strong><span style=\";font-family:Arial;font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">考试大纲<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．计算机系统概述<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 了解计算机的发展历程；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握冯·诺依曼计算机结构的特点，计算机硬件的基本组成与功能，计算机系统的组成（硬件<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">软件）及其层次结构，计算机的工作原理；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握计算机的性能指标，具体包括<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">执行时间、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPI<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、时钟周期、主频等； <\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．运算方法与运算部件<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）掌握数制与编码：包括进位计数制及其相互转换，真值和机器数，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">BCD<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">编码，字符与字符串；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 熟练掌握定点数的表示、运算与运算部件：包括无符号数的表示和有符号整数的表示；补码定点数加减法运算；定点数乘除运算；识记溢出概念和判别方法；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握浮点数的表示与运算：包括浮点数的表示，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">IEEE754<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">标准，浮点数的加减运算及其规格化； <\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）理解算术逻辑单元<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ALU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的功能与结构，掌握补码加减运算器如何实现；并能够对典型指令完成设计与实现；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握不同层次程序员看到的运算：高级语言以<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">C<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">语言为例，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">ISA<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">层面则以<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">MIPS32<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为例；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．存储器分层体系结构<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）掌握存储系统的分层，半导体随机访问存储器的组织，只读存储器及主存的主要技术指标等；理解存储器芯片与<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的连接，掌握多模块存储器的交叉存储；<\/span><\/span> <\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）掌握高速缓冲存储器的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">基本访存过程， <\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Cache<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和主存之间的映射方式，程序访问的局部性原理对编程的影响及<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Cache-friendly<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的程序，理解<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Cache<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">替换算法和<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Cache<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">写策略；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）掌握虚拟存储器的基本概念，三种实现方案，缺页的处理及快表的工作原理，注意虚拟地址和物理地址的转换问题，如何查段表和页表；<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">TLB<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的原理和作用；平均访问时间的计算等。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．指令系统<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）熟练掌握指令的基本格式，包括定长操作码和扩展操作码的优缺点对比，采用扩展操作码方式指令数目的计算及设计； <\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）指令的寻址方式：识记有效地址的概念，理解数据寻址和指令寻址，掌握常见寻址方式及寻址过程；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 理解<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CISC<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">RISC<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的基本概念及区别；掌握以<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">MIPS 32<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">为代表的指令集的典型指令，并能够完成相应的汇编程序设计。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">5<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．中央处理器<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）熟练掌握指令的执行过程，并考察一条指令执行的各个步骤；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">数据通路的功能及结构，掌握控制器的功能和设计，并能为<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">MIPS32<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的典型指令完成相应的<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">CPU<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">设计，包括单周期及流水体系结构的设计；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 掌握异常与中断的处理机制及相应的设计与实现；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">6<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">． 系统总线<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）了解总线概述：识记总线的基本概念，分类，总线的组成及性能指标；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） &nbsp;掌握总线仲裁的仲裁方式以及各自的工作原理；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） &nbsp;掌握总线操作和定时方式以及原理；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） &nbsp;了解总线标准，常用标准所规定的机械结构、功能结构和电气规范；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">7<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．输入输出组织<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）了解<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I/O<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统基本概念 <\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 识记各种外部设备，理解这些设备的基本工作原理和常见的性能指标；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 识记<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I/O<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">接口的功能和基本结构，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I/O<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">端口及其编址；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">） 熟练掌握<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I/O<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的三种控制方式；中断方式要求掌握中断的基本概念，中断响应过程，中断处理过程，多重中断和中断屏蔽等；<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">DMA<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方式要求掌握<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">DMA<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">控制器的组成和<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">DMA<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的传送过程。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","1BADEB547E1820C8E0632D1E000AB135":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">参考书目<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">《政治学原理<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">(<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第三版<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">)<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">》<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">(<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">新编<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">21<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">世纪公共管理系列教材<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">)<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">，景跃进、张小劲等主编，中国人民大学出版社，<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2015<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">01<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月版<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">考试内容<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">篇 政治的性质与政治研究<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">章 政治的性质与核心问题<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1.1 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">如何理解政治<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1.2 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">政治的核心概念与核心问题<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">章 政治学：研究方法与学科特点<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2.1 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">如何研究政治：历史的维度<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2.2 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">如何研究政治：逻辑的维度<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2.3 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">政治学的学科特点<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">篇 政治系统的硬件：国家与政府设置<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">章 国家和超国家政治<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3.1 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">从城邦国家到民族国家<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3.2 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">国家的形式<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3.3 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">国家与社会的关系<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3.4 <\/span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">民族国家面临的挑战<\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 方正仿宋简体;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第<\/span><span style=\"font-family: