gin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第四部分<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">: 法译汉<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">：<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">25分）<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">旨在测试考生的综合运用水平以及法语译成汉语的能力。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此部分共五个句子，每句五分，共计<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">25分， 考试时间为40分钟。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第五部分<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">: 汉译法<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">：<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">25分）<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">旨在测试考生的综合运用水平以及汉语译成法语的能力。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:5px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:5px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">此部分共五个句子，每句五分，共计<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">25分， 考试时间为40分钟。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p s