size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分类<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">和确定方法<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">了解光学<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">系统景深<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">的概念。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">5.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握像差<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">概念及分类；了解用于计算像差的光线光路计算公式。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">6.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握放大镜、显微镜、望远镜等典型光学系统的光学参数、结构形式、光束限制和成像特性<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">7.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">麦克斯韦方程组<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">及<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物质方程的表达式及物理意义；掌握<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">单色<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">平面<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">光<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">波的表达式及<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">其<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">性质。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">8.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握光波干涉的条件及获得相干光波的方法；掌握杨氏双缝干涉和平板的<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">双光束干涉<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">的强度分布公式、条纹性质及典型应用<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握多光束干涉的强度分布公式、条纹性质及典型应用。<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">9.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握衍射的定义、衍射系统的构成和衍射的分类；掌握典型孔径夫琅和费衍射的光强分布公式及衍射图样特点；掌握衍射对光学系统分辨本领的影响；掌握衍射光栅及闪耀光栅的工作原理、光栅方程和性能指标。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\">10.&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">掌握偏振光的概念及产生偏振光的常用方法；掌握布儒斯特定律和<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">马吕斯定律；<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px\">会用惠更斯作图法确定光在双折射晶体中的传播方向；掌握典型偏振器件的工作原理和应用；会用琼斯矩阵表示偏振光和偏振器件，及求解偏振系统的出射光偏振态；掌握偏振光的变换和判定方法。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-left: 24px;line-height: 150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 150%\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《光电信息工程基础》第二部分<\/span> &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通信原理（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分）<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">一．概论<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解通信系统的基本模型、分类，熟练掌握信息及其度量，通信性能指标。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">二．信道和噪声<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解随机过程的概念与描述，掌握信道的定义、信道的数学模型、信道的分类、信道特性对信号传输的影响，了解通信系统中的噪声，掌握信道容量及香农公式。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">三．模拟调制系统<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">掌握幅度调制原理、掌握非线性调制原理；<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">四．数字基带传输系统<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">掌握数字基带信号及其频谱特性、基带传输常用码型、数字基带信号传输与码间串扰、无码间串扰的基带传输特性、眼图。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">五．数字带通传输系统<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">掌握二进制数字调制原理、二进制数字调制系统的抗噪声性能、二进制数字调制系统的性能比较，了解多进制数字调制原理。<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">六．数字信号的最佳接收机<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解数字信号的统计特性、数字信号的最佳接收机、确知数字信号的最佳接收机、确知数字信号最佳接收机的误码率，掌握数字信号的匹配滤波器接收法。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">七．掌握模拟信号的抽样、模拟脉冲调制和抽样信号的量化。<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">八．掌握纠错编码的基本原理、纠错编码的性能、简单的实用编码、线性分组码和循环码。<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《光电信息工程基础》第三部分<\/span> &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">《数字图像处理》<\/span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">50<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分）<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、掌握图像处理与分析的基本概念；了解<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">图像处理与分析技术的形成与发展<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；了解图像处理与分析技术应用。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、了解图像数字化基础；掌握数字图像的性质及其分析方法。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">3<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">、掌握图像压缩的基本概念和算法，包括<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">Huffman<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">编码、算术编码等，了解<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">JPEG<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">压缩算法。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">4<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">、掌握图像几何变换类型与数学表达形式；了解图像正交变换基本算法概念，包括离散傅里叶变换、<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">K-L<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">变换、小波变换等；熟练掌握灰度直方图的定义、计算方法及其在灰度变换、二值化等图像处理中的应用。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">5<\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">、熟练掌握图像卷积操作的定义和计算方法，熟悉常见的图像卷积模板及其在图像增强、平滑、锐化、特征提取等方面的应用。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">掌握<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">图<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">像预处理的基本算法，包括增强、平滑、<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">锐化<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等；掌握图像分割算法，包括阈值处理、边缘处理、区域处理、模板处理；<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">了解图像退化模型和图像复原算法，包括运动模糊退化估计、维纳滤波、等功率谱滤波等。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、掌握数学形态学的基本概念；了解图像处理中形态学的具体结构与表达。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、理解各种图像解译方法；掌握<\/span>SIFT<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">HOG<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">Hough<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、监督分类与非监督分类等常规分析算法；<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">了解基于深度学习的图像解译算法的优势与局限<\/span><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\">9<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、<\/span><\/span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解图像处理算法在遥感图像地物分类、目标检测中的应用，掌握传统方法<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">K-means<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和深度学习方法<\/span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">U-net<\/span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的算法流程及各自特点。<\/span><\/span><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体\"><\/span><br/><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 150%\"><br/><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\"><\/span><br/><\/p><p style=\"line-height: 150%\">参考书目：<\/p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体;color:black\"><\/span><\/strong><\/p><p style=\";line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px