\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">力的投影，平面汇交力系的合成与平衡，平面力对点的矩，平面力偶理论。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">3&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">平面任意力系<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">力线平移定理，平面力系简化理论，主矢，主矩，平面任意力系的平衡方程及其应用，物体系统的平衡，平面桁架。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">4&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">空间任意力系<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">空间汇交力系，空间力对点的矩和对轴的矩，空间力偶理论，空间力系简化理论，主矢，主矩，空间任意力系的平衡方程及其应用，重心。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">5&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">摩擦<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">摩擦角与滚动摩阻的概念，考虑摩擦的平衡问题。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">（二）材料力学<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">1&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">拉伸、压缩与剪切<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握拉（压）杆的内力、应力、位移、变形和应变概念，直杆轴向拉伸或压缩时斜截面上的应力。掌握单向拉压的胡克定律，掌握材料的拉、压力学性能。掌握强度条件的概念及进行拉压强度和刚度计算。掌握轴向拉伸或压缩时的变形能，拉伸、压缩静不定问题，温度应力和装配应力。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">2&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">扭转<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握纯剪概念，剪切胡克定律，切应力互等定理。掌握圆轴扭转的内力，圆轴扭转应力和变形，建立强度和刚度条件，会进行扭转强度和刚度的计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">3&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">弯曲内力<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握平面弯曲内力概念，能够计算较复杂受载下的内力，会利用载荷集度、剪力和弯矩间的微分关系画内力图。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">4&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">弯曲应力<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握弯曲正应力和弯曲切应力概念，掌握弯曲强度计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">5&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">弯曲变形<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握弯曲变形有关概念，会用积分法求和叠加法求弯曲变形，会解简单静不定梁。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">6&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">应力和应变分析<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">强度理论<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">这是本课程的重点和难点。要求很好掌握平面应力状态下的应力分析方法，包括二向应力状态分析<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">——<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">解析法，二向应力状态分析<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">——<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">图解法；掌握三向应力状态下的主应力和最大切应力的概念；正确理解广义胡克定律并熟练运用；正确理解常用强度理论及其应用。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">7&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">组合变形<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握组合变形和叠加原理，掌握拉伸或压缩与弯曲的组合，扭转与弯曲的组合，及其它组合变形下杆件的强度计算，会进行复杂受载下杆件强度的分析。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">8&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">能量方法<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握外力功与弹性应变能的概念，会用互等定理，卡氏定理，虚功原理，单位载荷法，莫尔积分，计算莫尔积分的图乘法计算位移（掌握任一种方法即可）。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">9&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">静不定结构（超静定结构）<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握用力法解超静定结构的方法，会利用对称及反对称性质，掌握一次、二次超静定问题的计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">10&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">动载荷<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握动载荷问题中动静法的应用，杆件受冲击时的动荷系数、动应力和动变形的计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">11&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">压杆稳定<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握压杆稳定的概念，掌握两端铰支细长压杆的临界压力，其他支座条件下细长压杆的临界应力，欧拉公式的适用范围，经验公式和压杆的柔度的概念。会进行压杆稳定性计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">12&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">平面图形的几何性质<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0\"><span style=\";font-family:仿宋;color:rgb(58,80,100);font-size:16px\">掌握截面几何性质，重点掌握静矩、惯性矩、惯性积等概念和平行移轴公式。<\/span><\/p>","1BADEB547DFE20C8E0632D1E000AB135":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">考试大纲：<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">一、考查的知识范围<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">1．艺术学总论（艺术及其学科属性、艺术观念、艺术体制、艺术的本质与特征、艺术的起源、艺术的功能与艺术教育、文化系统中的艺术等）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">2．艺术种类（包括实用艺术、造型艺术、表情艺术、综合艺术、语言艺术等）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">3．艺术系统（艺术创作、艺术作品、艺术鉴赏、艺术发展、艺术消费、艺术批评等）。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">二、考试形式与试卷结构<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">1．答卷方式：闭卷，笔试。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">2．题型（但不限于）<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">（1）名词解释；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">（2）简答题；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">（3）鉴赏题；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">（4）材料分析题；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">（5）综合论述题。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">三、评分标准及要求：满分为150分<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap;\">．<\/span>客观题参考评分标准进行评判；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">2<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; text-wrap: wrap;\">．<\/span>主观题要求文字表述简洁流畅，书写认真，观点清楚，视角独特，逻辑清晰。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">四、参考书目（但不限于）：<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">1<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; te