&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）产品设计方法；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）产品设计的程序与开发过程；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）产品设计的评价。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">2.<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">设计创意<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">考查设计思维能力，要求思维具有合理的逻辑理性及跳跃的灵感思维，并在产品形体方案中有充分的体现。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">3.<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">产品构形<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">构形能力基本反映考生的审美观和艺术直觉，考生应能够把握造型要素和造型法则，并综合运用。具体要求为：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">1<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）能够掌握产品语意；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">2<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）处理好形体的协调与对比关系；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">3<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）灵活的思维，体现出不同设计方案之间的差异性；<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">4<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">）能够对产品的功能细节与结构细节做出简单的分析和判断。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">4.<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">相关制图<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">考生可以以自己熟练掌握的某种表现技法，表现设计思想。除设计题外，在理论题解答时，同样要求有图表来进行补充说明。此外，图形组合的版面效果，也是重点要求。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（二）试卷结构及考题形式<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">以主观题为主。本考试采用笔试方式，考试时间为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">180<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">分钟。考试试卷共分两部分：<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">第一部分<\/span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">设计概念理解（文字论述<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: &#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">+<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">图表）：<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; 1~3<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">道题，要求考生以自己的理解进行解答，可以有独特的视角。此题考察重点在知识面的广度与深度，包括：概念理解是否清晰，论证是否充分、详实，结构是否逻辑、严整。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">第二部分<\/span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">设计题（制图<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">+<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">文字、图表）：<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">1~2<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">道题，根据前一设计概念理解题，将概念理解落实到实际操作。以<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">2~3<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">个设计方案，表现设计思想，并进行适当文字说明。考察重点在创意和表现能力，方案可以并不完善，但要相对完整，功能、结构清晰不含糊。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">（三）试卷题型、题量、记分及答题时间<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">序号<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">题型<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">题量<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">记分<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">Ⅰ<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">设计概念理解（论述）<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1-3<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">道<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 20-30%<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">Ⅱ<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">设计题<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1-2<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">道<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;70-80%<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:auto;margin-bottom:auto;line-height:normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;color:#3A5064\">考试时间：<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">180<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#3A5064\">分钟，总分：<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;-webkit-standard&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;;color:#3A5064\">150<\/span><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","1BADEB547E2420C8E0632D1E000AB135":"<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">参考书目<\/span><\/strong>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、东南大学同济大学天津大学合编<\/span>. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">混凝土结构<\/span>.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中册<\/span>.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">混凝土结构与砌体结构设计（第五版）<\/span>. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国建筑工业出版社，<\/span>2012<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年<\/span><\/p><p>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、刘龄嘉主编<\/span>.&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桥梁工程<\/span>.&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">人民交通出版社<\/span>&nbsp; 2014.5<\/p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">考试内容：<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">涉及“混凝土结构”、“桥梁工程”<\/span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">门课程，具体包括：<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）混凝土结构设计的一般方法，楼盖（梁板结构），单层厂房（排架结构），多层框架结构。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）桥梁所受的作用及作用效应组合（第三章）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）简支梁桥上部结构构造及设计，桥面板计算，荷载横向分布及主梁内力计算（第五章）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）拱桥的分类、组成及构造设计、计算（第六章前五节）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）连续梁桥及连续刚构桥的特点、构造及设计，连续梁桥预应力次内力计算方法（第七章）；<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（<\/span>7<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）桥梁墩台的类型，重力式桥墩及桩柱式桥墩的计算（第八章）。<\/span><\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p><p><br/><\/p>","1BADEB547DEE20C8E0632D1E000AB135":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\"><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 80, 100); font-size: 18px; font-family: 仿宋;\"><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">（1）《民法学》（第二版），《民法学》编写组，高等教育出版社2022年8月版。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family:等线\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">（2）<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">《经济法学》（第三版），《经济法学》编写组，高等教育出版社2022年8月版。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">总体要求：要求考生全面掌握指定参考书目的主要内容，深刻理解相关法学理论与法律制度的内涵及其相互之间的逻辑关系，能够结合热点问题展开学理与法律适用分析。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 等线;\"><\/span><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">（<\/span><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">1）<\/span>民法部分<\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本部分考试内容主要包括：民法总论；物权法；合同法；人格权法；侵权责任法<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 等线;\"><\/span><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">（2）<\/span>经济法部分 &nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本部分考试内容主要包括：经济法学的研究对象、经济法学的产生和发展；经济法学的体系；经济法的概念和历史；经济法的体系和地位；经济法的宗旨和原则；经济法的主体和行为；经济法主体的权利 (力)义务和责任；经济法的制定与实施；宏观调控法的基本理论与制度；市场规制法的基本理论与制度；反垄断法律制度；反不正当竞争法律制度；消费者保护法律制度；质量、价格、广告和计量监管法律制度。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun;\">（注：民法、经济法在考试中各占部门法学总分的<\/span>50％。）<\/span><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\"><\/span><\/p><p><br/><\/p>","1BADEB547E4A20C8E0632D1E000AB135":"<p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 仿宋;\">《电磁场与微波技术》考试纲要（占40%）<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;text-indent:11px;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\">第一章 数学基础<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;text-indent:11px;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\">1、掌握矢量运算的加、减、点乘、叉乘、微积分等常规运算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;text-indent:11px;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\">2、掌握矢量的通量、环量、散度、旋度运算，掌握标量的梯度及方向导数运算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;text-indent:11px;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\">3、掌握基本的矢量恒等式运算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;第二章 静态场<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; 1、掌握静电场的高斯公式运算、基本方程、位函数、坡松方程、介质极化、边界条件以及电容计算。<\/span><\/p><p style=\"margin-top:4px;