与系统的频率响应<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">7.全通网络与最小相移网络<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">8.连续时间系统的模拟方框图及信号流图。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">五、离散系统的时域分析<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">1.抽样与理想抽样<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">2.离散时间信号与离散时间系统<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">3.离散时间系统的零输入响应和零状态响应<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">4.离散时间系统的冲激响应<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">5.离散卷积及其性质<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">6.离散时间系统的全响应<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">六、离散时间系统的复频域分析<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">1.z变换及其收敛域<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">2.z变换的性质及反z变换<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">3.离散时间系统的z域分析<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">4.离散时间系统的系统函数<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">5.离散时间系统的稳定性及其判别方法<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">6.离散时间系统的模拟方框图及信号流图。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\"><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\"><br/><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: 仿宋, SimSun;\">考试题型<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> <\/span><\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;1）选择题；2）简单计算题；3）综合分析计算题。<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-family: 仿宋, SimSun; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<br/><\/span><\/p><p><span 